{"tid":1432574,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日狗仔記招殺著！","createTime":"2019-08-08T09:16:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T09:29:29.000Z","uid":33709,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b1b6c2f9a8e8e9ec32194b3fa14777b2eccb0a93","tid":1432574,"uid":33709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:16:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">5. 指示威者應對意見不合 / 偷拍人士時，可能會干犯傷人、損壞他人財產 及「不誠實使用電腦」罪等。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n佢想屈我地會襲擊意見不合同影相既市民！<br />\n<br />\n大家記得有禮貌啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6533a767bef6366d4b8b90cd0efd84b3426dcf7c","tid":1432574,"uid":200062,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:16:40.000Z","msg":"禮貌行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99f62601571560cf18d24309e0a16e0dc786a88b","tid":1432574,"uid":33709,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:17:50.000Z","msg":"大家記得溫柔啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccadf6b5508b069651e3e28e66e8262e4c1648f9","tid":1432574,"uid":161350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:18:42.000Z","msg":"温柔地指責别人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e7274f43b794774e083db2dac06d7f7c455a859","tid":1432574,"uid":271407,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:20:51.000Z","msg":"Be humble"},{"pid":"372fa31a029704eb6c31bc3b21c024a84a7d2f05","tid":1432574,"uid":156327,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:22:09.000Z","msg":"你話我係五毛都好我都要澄清返<br />\n<br />\n協和小學案引發討論<br />\n<br />\n高等法院法官2018年8月駁回律政司就協和小學老師案的上訴時，曾指出取用電腦（access to a computer）及使用電腦（use a computer）是有分別的。因為案中的被告，是使用她們自己的手機犯案，法官認為立法原意是針對「進入電腦作出『犯罪行為』」，但控方現概括為任何取用電腦的情況，認為並不適合。因為案中各個被告，並沒有侵入他人電腦截取或使用內在的資料，只是用自己的手機拍照，並傳送應該保密的資料。認為本案性質上與案例中，罪犯在未授權下，進入他人的電腦盜取資料不同。故裁定律政司敗訴。<br />\n<br />\n協和小學試題外洩案　律政司求釐清不誠實取用電腦罪被裁上訴失敗<br />\n立法原意針對駭客<br />\n<br />\n而案件2019年2月在終審法院上訴時，法官亦提到，這罪的立法原意，是針對電腦駭客而製定，指侵入別人的電腦，並竄改或偷取資料，而非用以指控任何以電腦干犯的罪行。<br />\n<br />\n惟律政司過去卻常用這罪用以檢控任何使用電腦，或智能電話相關的罪行，除電腦黑客類的案件外，亦有用於手提電話偷拍裙底春光，以及在網路上號召市民參與可能非法的政治社會運動等。但自高等法院於去年8月頒下判詞之後，律政司隨即發出指引將有關的案件押後處理，以等待終審法院的終極指引，惟終院維持原判，並認為所涉範圍不應太廣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/301123/不誠實取用電腦案-律政司敗訴-一文看清甚麼罪受影響\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F301123%2F%E4%B8%8D%E8%AA%A0%E5%AF%A6%E5%8F%96%E7%94%A8%E9%9B%BB%E8%85%A6%E6%A1%88-%E5%BE%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%8F%B8%E6%95%97%E8%A8%B4-%E4%B8%80%E6%96%87%E7%9C%8B%E6%B8%85%E7%94%9A%E9%BA%BC%E7%BD%AA%E5%8F%97%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF&d=g7cViP25SqI%2F%2FE6cIGpO75nDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=1eb3bde5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/301123/不誠實取用電腦案-律政司敗訴-一文看清甚麼罪受影響</a><br />\n<br />\n補返條鈴比在大蛇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2eee24e318522f7cf60e9c835c668e4a60836d3","tid":1432574,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:23:09.000Z","msg":"黑警記者會終於講返句人話<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1432578\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1432578</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e30923d8c902bd4d65908a5bd7bbedea534a8b20","tid":1432574,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:23:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我建議文宣方向<br />\n<br />\n針對警方無差別襲擊，標籤為<span style=\"color: red;\">國家恐怖主義武裝組織</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n佢標籤我地做港獨，我地標籤返佢做「國家恐怖主義份子」 正名標籤警方為非法嘅武裝組織<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1426058\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1426058</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">認同請聯署請分享</span><br />\n已有24,309個簽名（8 Aug 2019 at 17:23）<br />\n［白宮聯署］香港警察為恐怖組織<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1427701\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1427701</a><br />\n<br />\n鼓勵遊行示威口號<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">HKPF IS STATE TERRORIST!<br />\nNO STATE TERRORISM!<br />\nNO INDISCRIMINATE ATTACK!<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"10d687a08d5695b01c2cedcc507282c369b7938f","tid":1432574,"uid":45332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:24:33.000Z","msg":"依條罪唔係要用人地電腦先入到咩？<br />\n用自己電腦告唔入架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"625a0a068ad89ffcd9d305915909aa1450792b7b","tid":1432574,"uid":33709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10d687a08d5695b01c2cedcc507282c369b7938f","tid":1432574,"uid":45332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:24:33.000Z","msg":"依條罪唔係要用人地電腦先入到咩？<br />\n用自己電腦告唔入架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:25:34.000Z","msg":"靠嚇 呀蛇毅進仔邊識咁多法律<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e302992a9cfb8861fadd2c5ea1c757a2d60d6e3b","tid":1432574,"uid":296084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:27:39.000Z","msg":"提醒唔好影大頭<br />\n同埋好心啦　做好自己先<br />\n包好自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dab62249aa79859bc98b9d12a4b9986e362a1162","tid":1432574,"uid":278201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:29:29.000Z","msg":"推"}]}